  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob, P</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You turn on the spot, revolving to create a whirling, dangerous dance. You may move up to your full movement speed, gaining a +4 deflection bonus to Defense against any attacks of opportunity made against you. As you move, you can make a single attack at each creature you pass, up to one creature per two levels (maximum 5), though you must move at least 5 ft between attacks. Creatures affected must make a Spot check (DC 10) to avoid losing their Dexterity bonus to Defense against the attack, though you cannot apply sneak attack damage to the attacks.<br><br>You become nauseated for 1 round after completing this technique (Fortitude, DC 11 + 2 per attack made negates).</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
